f=\"/cn/word/keratin\">keratin</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of kerato- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/kerato-\">kerato-</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of migraine \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/migraine\">migraine</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of monoceros \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/monoceros\">monoceros</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of reindeer \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/reindeer\">reindeer</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of rhinoceros \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/rhinoceros\">rhinoceros</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of saveloy \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/saveloy\">saveloy</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of serval \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/serval\">serval</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of triceratops \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/triceratops\">triceratops</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of unicorn \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/unicorn\">unicorn</a>。</p><p>这个词汇源于假设存在的语言祖先，并通过以下实例得到证明：梵语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">srngam</i> “角”； 波斯语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">sar</i> “头”，阿维斯塔语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">sarah-</i> \"头\"； 希腊语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">karnon</i> “角”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">koryne</i> “棍，狼牙棒”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">koryphe</i> “头”； 拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">cornu</i> “角”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">cervus</i> “鹿”； 古英语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">horn</i> “动物的角”； 威尔士语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">carw</i> “鹿”。</p>"
